byline.original: By Telegraph to The New-York Times

lead_paragraph: The following additional returns of the Georgia election have been received here. Union Majorities.--Chatham, 82; McIntosh, 40; Muscogee. 178; Richmond, 202: Houston, 167; Morgan, 150; Taliaferro, 280; Burke, 150; DeKath, 800; Pike 35; Monroe, 50; Walton, 325; Grenne, 545; Clarke, 205; Wilkes, 125; Warren, 245; Newbern, 700. Two Precincts to be heard from.
